items.name: quantum4j
items.description: Quantum4J is a pure-Java quantum computing framework designed to bring quantum programming to the JVM ecosystem. It provides a clean, intuitive API similar to Qiskit, a fast state-vector simulator, a QASM exporter, and a growing set of standard quantum gates.
